        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Doctor:</strong> Dr. {{data.doctorName}}</li>
          <li><strong>Doctor Email:</strong> {{data.doctorEmail}}</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          You will receive an email reminder closer to the appointment time. If
          you need to reschedule, please contact us as soon as possible.
        </p>
        <p>
          Thank you for choosing Safe Mind.
        </p>
      </div>
